# KimiFlare Cost Tracking Demo
# Shows the /cost command with gateway-confirmed totals and cache hit ratio
# Output: docs/demos/cost-tracking.gif

Output docs/demos/cost-tracking.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "bash demos/scripts/cost-tracking.sh"
Enter
Sleep 8s
